@prefix : <http://example.org/diamond#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

:A a owl:Class .
:B a owl:Class .
:C a owl:Class .
:D a owl:Class .

:B rdfs:subClassOf :A .
:C rdfs:subClassOf :A .
:D rdfs:subClassOf :B .
:D rdfs:subClassOf :C .
